window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Ga'ee escaped, but aren't on the run.</p> <p>They are coming back, and when they return, it'll be with a vast armada of ten-kilometer-long ships with millions of drones.</p> <p>Next time would be for real.</p> <p>The invasion would mean the end of all life.</p> <p>Earth Fleet must rally the seven races.</p> <p>And Declan Payne and his team are at the front of the fight as Leviathan goes to war.</p> <p>While goliaths wrestle, the galaxy's fate hinges on the decisions of a small group of people putting their lives on the line for those who won't.</p>"; 
